http://amazingdiscoveries.tv/media/93/606-the-joyous-funeral/
http://amazingdiscoveries.org/

Death can bring life. Joy can replace doom and despondency. Freedom can win out over slavery. This is good news.

Discover one of the most beautiful truths in the Bible: how a funeral can be joyous. This is one time where you can be excited at a funeral. A look at what the Bible says about getting a new life in Christ.
